original_title: The Women of Cell Block F
overview: PRISON... an image of lonely solitude with absolutely no pleasures perceived whatsoever. But, at Cell Block F, the warden has other plans for his nasty inmates.  "THE GIRLS OF CELL BLOCK F" explodes with enough erotic energy, that surely you'll want to be locked up in this minimum security prison.  Gorgeous, sex-starved jailhouse harlots disrupt the decadent prison, and transform it into a lust-drenched breeding ground for carnal desires. Everyone, from the prisoners to the wicked warden get their orgasmic cravings quenched, while upholding the sacred Law of Lust!
tagline: You can lock them up, but you can't keep them down!
title: The Women of Cell Block F
